No. 574. Robert S. Bright, Trustee, Petitioner, v. The Fifth Congregational Church of Washington, D. C. March 4, 1907. Mr. Héber J. May and Mr. S. Herbert Giesy for petitioner. Mr. W. C. Sullivan for respondent.

Petition for. a writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of the District of Columbia denied.
